OL,3,CHow the war in the Middle East is now
OL,4,Cimpacting Channel Island airshows
OL,6,FThe Red Arrows will return to the
OL,7,Fskies in both the Jersey and Guernsey
OL,8,Fairshows this year, despite mounting
OL,9,Fconcerns over fuel prices impacting
OL,10,Fboth displays.
OL,12,FJersey's International Air Display
OL,13,Forganiser, Mike Higgins, revealed
OL,14,Fexclusively to ITV News on Wednesday
OL,15,F(22 April) that the Arrows would be
OL,16,Fparticipating in the Channel Islands
OL,17,Fdisplays once again this year.
OL,19,FThe Arrows closed both of the Channel
OL,20,FIslands' Air Shows last year, and are
OL,21,Fa fan favourite attraction.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
