OL,3,CHow the war in the Middle East is now
OL,4,Cimpacting Channel Island airshows
OL,6,FLast year, Jersey's air display
OL,7,Ffeatured more than twenty planes;
OL,8,Fhowever, approximately half have been
OL,9,Fbooked so far this year, as the
OL,10,Forganiser cannot forecast the cost of
OL,11,Fhiring more planes.
OL,13,FWith the ongoing conflict in Iran
OL,14,Fdriving up worldwide aviation fuel
OL,15,Fprices, it is currently unclear how
OL,16,Fmany more planes will be confirmed to
OL,17,Ffeature in both displays.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
