OL,3,CHow the war in the Middle East is now
OL,4,Cimpacting Channel Island airshows
OL,6,FThe Guernsey Air Display is set to
OL,7,Ftake place on Wednesday 9 September,
OL,8,Fwith Jersey's International Air
OL,9,FDisplay due to run the day after.
OL,11,FHowever, the final line-ups for both
OL,12,Fdisplays are unlikely to be confirmed
OL,13,Funtil late August due to ongoing
OL,14,Fmarket volatility.
OL,16,FMike Higgins said: "Fuel prices have
OL,17,Fgone up 53% for Jet A1 fuel since last
OL,18,Fyear."
OL,20,FHe added: "We have no idea what the
OL,21,Ffuel price will be.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
