OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777291866
OL,3,CHow the war in the Middle East is now
OL,4,Cimpacting Channel Island airshows
OL,6,F"I have to look at what we can put
OL,7,Finto the show - jets in particular are
OL,8,Fa concern because of the cost and
OL,9,Fquantity of their fuel required."
OL,11,FBy contrast, Guernsey's Air Display is
OL,12,Fless likely to be impacted by Jet fuel
OL,13,Fcosts.
OL,15,F"We obviously have a much smaller
OL,16,Fdisplay than they (Jersey) do, with
OL,17,Fonly about five or six items," Natalie
OL,18,FDavidson, Guernsey's Airshow organiser
OL,19,Ftold ITV News.
OL,26,@xD@SpmxD@Zpn
