OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777291866
OL,3,CHow the war in the Middle East is now
OL,4,Cimpacting Channel Island airshows
OL,6,FShe added: "As a result, our fuel
OL,7,Fcosts are much smaller.
OL,9,F"And often our displays have full
OL,10,Fprice packages, which include their
OL,11,Ffee and their fuel, so we're not as
OL,12,Fsusceptible to fuel cost rises."
OL,14,FThe RAF also charges for the Red
OL,15,FArrows using an all-inclusive price,
OL,16,Fmeaning organisers for both shows can
OL,17,Fplan and account for their cost in
OL,18,Fadvance.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
