OL,3,CHow the war in the Middle East is now
OL,4,Cimpacting Channel Island airshows
OL,6,FAirlines are less likely to be
OL,7,Faffected by volatility in fuel prices
OL,8,Fthan air shows are, because they can
OL,9,Fhedge these costs.
OL,11,FThis means locking in at a fixed price
OL,12,Fregardless of the market, which
OL,13,Fsmaller airshows (like those in the
OL,14,FChannel Islands) cannot feasibly do.
OL,16,FInstead, event organisers have to pay
OL,17,Ffor the fuel, as and when they need it
OL,18,F- leaving them vulnerable to price
OL,19,Fhikes determined by external factors.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
